highlights.description: We tend to not listen when we hear something we don't agree with
Madison is easy to get around
The city is alive with activities
UW campus seems very diverse to me, coming from a community in northern WI
Conversation about political correctness and the words we use to address each other
My hope is that we have opportunities and openness to listen and accept each other more
I want my representatives to remember providing basic services are their real job
I hope other LVN conversations bring in diverse voices

title: Strangers discover commonalities AND differences - Madison, WI 98
